\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee772e5f5133e8b64c7ef5dea66f9dd518473f5","tid":371140,"uid":36097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"鳳姐殺手08年末09年初連環殺人案<br />\n2008年11月23日凌晨時分，43歲鳳姐許彥香被發現倒斃於荃灣新村街36號鳳樓內，後腦曾遭重擊而大量出血，頸部懷疑被勒過，上半身蓋著染血毛巾，僅穿睡衣及內褲，警方調查後，懷疑死者被虐打致死。<br />\n荃灣凶案揭發後4天，「鳳姐殺手」直闖觀塘康寧道42號鳳樓，向46歲鳳姐孫╳珍聲稱是早前殺鳳姐案的真凶，作案時遇反抗，其後落荒而逃。涉案劫匪約5呎6吋高，事發時穿藍色上衣、黃色褲，戴帽及背斜袋，遇劫鳳姐形容歹徒力大無窮，用拇指及食掐住其頸項，令她幾乎窒息。"},{"pid":"f575a02616a98d26dce711655280e837f6c16c7a","tid":371140,"uid":30028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"要loop 幾多次"},{"pid":"29550b07fe81012f9293468f26fcbc8e2df3175a","tid":371140,"uid":3739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心理學話兇手好鍾意塊返犯案現場回味嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有證據就報警捉人啦"},{"pid":"3fa26b72ae57c3f60ff56f3e3cea7010fd8534df","tid":371140,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec78b7238a9e9e4c174664a0d6b61183c1c12ded","tid":371140,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"504c6d7aaeea484c0cb017f71482a9890fd4bb99","tid":371140,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ad881feeabf601c6370d2df51a114ad7160038","tid":371140,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9638ebf29e0deb281fd58632081da5f882282077","tid":371140,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re